Help for BADWORDS:

BADWORDS maintains a list of glob strings that every word
in a channel will be checked against (if BLOCKBADWORDS is set).

The ACTION parameter can be: KICK, WARN, BAN, KICKBAN or (if your
IRCd supports it) QUIET.

構文: BADWORDS <#channel> LIST
構文: BADWORDS <#channel> ADD <word> <action>
構文: BADWORDS <#channel> DEL <word>

コマンド例:
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #atheme LIST
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #sailors ADD f?ck kick
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #sailors ADD *dam?it* quiet
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #desensitized DEL f?ck
